pass does keep an index to make searching easier and faster
  details: one file is kept in passwordstore called .index.gpg
           this file will be updated by corresponding elements
		 and kept in sync with the repository

Usage: pass index action
Valid actions are: 
    update|recreate|create: 	updates the index
    edit: 			edits password and updates index
    insert:			generates new password and updates index
    mv: 				moves password and updates index
    rm: 				removes password and updates index
    find: 			searches for password returns matching entry names
    grep: 			searches for password returns lines in entries
